fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 added 33.10 points or 0.16% to settle at 20,103.10. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, tumbled 4.31% to 11.32. HDFC Bank, Reliance Industries (RIL) and State Bank of India (SBI) were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The September 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 28 September 2023.
